164
00:13:09,560 --> 00:13:16,700
That girl has no resolve, I tell you.
She can't keep at anything for long.

165
00:13:16,700 --> 00:13:19,150
- Mother, please -
- My, I almost forgot!

166
00:13:19,150 --> 00:13:22,760
The neighbors gave me some pastries.

167
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:26,670
Let me grab some to accompany our tea.

168
00:13:32,320 --> 00:13:35,160
How could she say that
about her own daughter?

169
00:13:35,160 --> 00:13:38,460
All she's done is humiliate Sayaka.

170
00:13:38,460 --> 00:13:42,580
It's a bit much,
even under the pretext of "acting humble".

171
00:13:42,580 --> 00:13:44,110
Yeah.

172
00:13:44,710 --> 00:13:50,270
That toxic mother doesn't love Sayaka.

173
00:13:51,650 --> 00:13:53,650
Now I'm sure of it.

174
00:13:55,830 --> 00:13:59,040
She's the one who hurt Sayaka.

175
00:14:00,280 --> 00:14:01,690
What are you doing?

176
00:14:01,690 --> 00:14:03,170
My, what happened?

177
00:14:03,170 --> 00:14:05,400
I'm sorry, I spilled a bit of my tea.

178
00:14:05,400 --> 00:14:07,910
You should wash that right away.

179
00:14:07,910 --> 00:14:09,880
I suppose so.

180
00:14:09,880 --> 00:14:12,650
I'll head to the restroom.

181
00:14:19,750 --> 00:14:21,840
Here you go.

182
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:23,760
Thank you.

183
00:14:40,840 --> 00:14:42,560
Excuse me.

184
00:14:42,560 --> 00:14:43,550
Yes?

185
00:14:43,550 --> 00:14:47,100
These are wonderful albums.

186
00:14:47,100 --> 00:14:48,660
- Really?
- Yes.

187
00:14:48,660 --> 00:14:52,640
I can see your love for your daughter
reflected in them.

188
00:14:52,640 --> 00:14:55,750
Hayashida is a wonderful match for her.

189
00:14:55,750 --> 00:14:59,760
He cares greatly for Sayaka.

190
00:14:59,760 --> 00:15:04,700
Yes. He graduated from an excellent school,
and has a promising career.

191
00:15:04,700 --> 00:15:08,120
I'm truly glad my daughter -

192
00:15:10,840 --> 00:15:13,200
Kazuomi?

193
