Are these from Sayaka's recitals?

194
00:15:19,750 --> 00:15:24,020
Yes, they are.
She won her first when she was seven.

195
00:15:24,020 --> 00:15:26,750
I see. That's amazing.

196
00:15:26,750 --> 00:15:30,570
I've always loved the violin,
ever since I was a young girl.

197
00:15:30,570 --> 00:15:33,470
Like mother, like daughter, no?

