199
00:15:49,600 --> 00:15:51,760
What are you doing?

200
00:15:57,510 --> 00:16:01,220
Kazuomi, tell me what's going on.

201
00:16:01,220 --> 00:16:02,790
Well...

202
00:16:02,790 --> 00:16:08,100
I thought you two were acting strange.

203
00:16:08,100 --> 00:16:13,900
