204
00:16:14,510 --> 00:16:15,960
Mother, I...

205
00:16:15,960 --> 00:16:18,390
Why have you really come today?

206
00:16:26,330 --> 00:16:30,910
Mother. What sort of medication is that?

207
00:16:34,290 --> 00:16:37,540
Your psychiatrist prescribed them,
did they not?

208
00:16:38,680 --> 00:16:43,830
Yes. The whole affair at the wedding
affected me significantly.

209
00:16:43,830 --> 00:16:46,750
Then are those sleeping pills?

210
00:16:46,750 --> 00:16:49,930
Why do you want to know?

211
00:16:49,930 --> 00:16:53,200
The reason Sayaka collapsed...

212
00:16:54,440 --> 00:16:57,120
wasn't solely because of an ulcer.

213
00:16:57,120 --> 00:16:58,670
What?

214
00:16:58,670 --> 00:17:03,650
Someone drugged her.

215
00:17:04,400 --> 00:17:06,620
Drugged her?

216
00:17:06,620 --> 00:17:09,440
<i>Sayaka!</i>

217
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:11,660
Kazuomi...

218
00:17:12,970 --> 00:17:17,630
Are you suspecting I did such a thing?

219
00:17:17,630 --> 00:17:19,000
We simply want to confirm -

220
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:22,330
I would never.
This is a psychotropic medication.

221
00:17:22,330 --> 00:17:23,630
Then please, show us the contents.

222
00:17:23,630 --> 00:17:25,630
Enough!

223
00:17:28,040 --> 00:17:33,710
You think I hurt Sayaka?

224
00:17:34,880 --> 00:17:38,420
The absolute disrespect.

225
00:17:40,260 --> 00:17:43,440
Do not even jest.

226
00:17:43,440 --> 00:17:50,210
You two could never understand how I felt
raising my child.

227
00:17:50,210 --> 00:17:58,570
I have lived my very life for Sayaka's sake.

228
00:17:59,330 --> 00:18:03,770
I have sacrificed everything
for her happiness.

229
00:18:03,770 --> 00:18:07,020
I'd be there for her. I'd worry for her.

230
00:18:07,020 --> 00:18:10,240
I gave up many things for her.

231
00:18:10,240 --> 00:18:17,140
And yet that child has betrayed
my every expectation.

232
00:18:20,880 --> 00:18:27,360
Even so, I love my daughter
from the bottom of my heart.

233
00:18:28,110 --> 00:18:34,060
I would never harm my own child.

234
00:18:36,920 --> 00:18:38,710
Mother...

235
00:18:47,120 --> 00:18:49,600
Just, wow.

236
00:18:54,450 --> 00:18:56,160
Excuse me?

237
00:19:01,060 --> 00:19:02,960
